ndard REPL with <a href=\"http://psysh.org/\">PsySH</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-12T07:37:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials &#x26; guides</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlxbRYpZdQg\">Siteground Webinar: Learn How WP-CLI Can Make Your Life Easier</a> - Practical examples on how you can improve your workflows with WP-CLI.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-11T19:31:36.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Third-party packages</h2><h3>Notable packages</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Yoast/wp-cli-faker\">Yoast/wp-cli-faker</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Yoast/wp-cli-faker\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">32</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":32,\"repo\":\"Yoast/wp-cli-faker\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Generate fake WordPress and WooCommerce content for testing purposes.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T16:03:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Third-party packages</h2><h3>Notable packages</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/aaemnnosttv/wp-cli-login-command\">aaemnnosttv/wp-cli-login-command</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/aaemnnosttv/wp-cli-login-command\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">202</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":202,\"repo\":\"aaemnnosttv/wp-cli-login-command\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Login to WordPress with secure passwordless magic links.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T16:03:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials &#x26; guides</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://pascalbirchler.com/an-introduction-to-wp-cli/\">An Introduction to WP-CLI</a> - Introductory article that introduces the main concepts and some popular use cases of WP-CLI.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T16:03:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials &#x26; guides</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.tv/2017/05/22/alain-schlesser-controlling-wordpress-through-the-command-line-introduction-to-wp-cli/\">Controlling WordPress through the Command Line</a> - Introductory talk that covers the very basics of the command line for people who never used the console before.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T16:03:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials &#x26; guides</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://guides.wp-bullet.com/category/wp-cli/\">WP Bullet WP-CLI Guides</a> - Snippet-based guides that solve specific use cases.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T16:03:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Official links</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://wp-cli.org/\">wp-cli.org</a> - Homepage of the WP-CLI project.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T15:34:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Official links</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/handbook/\">WP-CLI handbook</a> - Guides on how to use or extend WP-CLI.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T15:34:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Official links</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/cli/commands/\">WP-CLI command reference</a> - Reference documentation for all the official WP-CLI commands.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T15:34:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Official links</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/\">Make WordPress.org - CLI</a> - Main entry point for contributing to WP-CLI.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/handbook/contributing/\">Contributing guide</a> - Everything you need to know to contribute to the tool or its infrastructure.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/chat/\">Official MakeWP Slack</a> - Official Slack team where all international contributions to WordPress and its teams are discussed.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://wordpress.slack.com/messages/cli/\">#cli channel</a> - The official support channel for WP-CLI and the WordPress CLI team.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/cli/good-first-issues/\">Good first issues</a> - List of issues on that are limited in scope and complexity.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T15:34:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Official links</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli\">WP-CLI GitHub organization</a> - Canonical home of the WP-CLI source code.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli\">WP-CLI framework repository</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.4k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":4358,\"repo\":\"wp-cli/wp-cli\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - The source code for the WP-CLI framework that powers all of the commands.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-bundle\">WP-CLI bundle repository</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-bundle\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">41</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":41,\"repo\":\"wp-cli/wp-cli-bundle\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - The source for the WP-CLI \"binary\" and how it is assembled.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-tests\">WP-CLI tests repository</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/wp-cli/wp-cli-tests\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">15</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":15,\"repo\":\"wp-cli/wp-cli-tests\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - The testing framework used throughout all WP-CLI repositories.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T15:34:38.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/iipc/awesome-web-archiving","repo":"iipc/awesome-web-archiving"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/mourarthur/awesome-credit-modeling","repo